{
  "stem": "1603.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- however, there was a party in Hungary like you have here now, the skinheads, called the Arrow Cross Party in Hungary, which was the skinheads.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You call them Nazis or skinheads.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And a man named Szalasi was the leader, and he took over.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he was even more-- more sadistic than the Gestapo and the Germans were, and so on.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And so from then on, we had to go into hiding, 100%.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We couldn't stay in that apartment where-- where our maid was staying.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So what happened, we all split up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "My father went back to-- to the ambulance service, where he was driving then an ambulance.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "My sister and my mother went up to hide out with nuns.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I was hiding separately, by myself, in a Catholic school.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And that's where I was hiding for a long time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I was extremely bored.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It's stupid, but I'm saying.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But I was bored.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And so I thought, I'm-- I'm not gonna to stay here, I'm going to go out for a walk.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And oh, I could [INAUDIBLE] chances with the Nazis and the Arrow Head people and everything-- not Arrow Head, Arrow Cross, Arrow Cross.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And so I just went out on the street, and I said, I'm gonna go and see a movie.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So I walked about three miles to a movie.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I-- I was familiar with the movie house.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And this is some story, and some interest, but nobody ever can explain what really happened here.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But that's why my sister is alive today.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "What happened was that I was walking to this movie house, and-- and the movie house was bombed to the ground.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I was so shocked, and I said-- that I was just standing there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I didn't-- I didn't go anywhere.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
